title: 101: Rams-Titans trade fallout & favorite player by round
itunes:title: 101: Rams-Titans trade fallout & favorite player by round
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks react to the blockbuster trade for the first overall pick between the Titans and Rams. The guys then give you their personal favorite players in the draft round by round. DJ and Bucky then wrap the show by breaking down their cornerback Red Stars of the Week and Bucky's latest mock draft.
